Video Stream Server Benchmark: postfix + smtp-source

1. Install the postfix in the server:
	sudo apt-get install postfix

2. Configure postfix in /etc/postfix/main.cf
	add: resolve_numeric_domain = yes

3. Reload postfix:
	/etc/init.d/postfix reload

4. Install the postfix in the client:
	sudo apt-get install postfix

5. Configure postfix in /etc/postfix/main.cf
	add: resolve_numeric_domain = yes

6. Reload postfix:
	/etc/init.d/postfix reload

7. Generate and mail from client to server:
	smtp-source -s 20 -l 5120000 -m 200 -c -f root@10.4.128.4 -t root@10.4.128.2 10.4.128.2:25
